                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-22-off130 t18190421-22-crimeloc132"></join>, 50 yards of carpet, value 6 l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190421-22-victim258" type="victimName">
                           Daniel Edward 
                           Colston
                        <interp inst="t18190421-22-victim258" type="surname" value="Colston"></interp>
